& =11 \times 10 \times 8 \times 3-11 \times 3 \times 4 \times 7 \\\\
& =11 \times 3 \times 4[20-7] \\\\
& =11 \times 12 \times 13=(12-1) \times 12 \times(12+1) \\\\
& =12\left(12^2-1\right)=12^3-12
\end{aligned}
$$

